{"tid":795271,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如果真係想環保 點解要淨係唔比用吸管","createTime":"2018-08-27T01:15:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T14:03:39.000Z","uid":35217,"like":32,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"821b0cc5018e51c281180717e2c1c94ca3be9e83","tid":795271,"uid":35217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:15:39.000Z","msg":"M記k記d堂食餐具全部都即棄嘅<br />\n係想環保嘅就應該規定佢地堂食唔準用膠刀膠叉紙杯紙盒etc<br />\n一定環保過唔用吸管n倍<br />\n況且唔用吸管會對食客造成不便 但轉用非即棄餐具基本上唔會有影響<br />\n係m記k記想慳皮 唔想請人洗碗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nd商家借環保為名縮皮 <br />\nd所謂環保份子又助紂為虐<br />\n根本唔係解決問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利伸：我支持環保 個人黎講用唔用吸管都冇乜所謂"},{"pid":"af675bba6f04fe9ac879920edc14ce7dd2833a6a","tid":795271,"uid":180156,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:21:15.000Z","msg":"其實商家點解要理會環保撚"},{"pid":"93adac38e82c590efc245f56ed22c8fd0499db51","tid":795271,"uid":10998,"like":20,"dislike":3,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:25:17.000Z","msg":"咩叫吸管？<br />\n<br />\n讀得書少淨係知飲管"},{"pid":"a2c0dfe06254495f1ea775b5a7e322f61d7051d5","tid":795271,"uid":35217,"like":3,"dislike":18,"score":-15,"quote":{"pid":"93adac38e82c590efc245f56ed22c8fd0499db51","tid":795271,"uid":10998,"like":20,"dislike":3,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:25:17.000Z","msg":"咩叫吸管？<br />\n<br />\n讀得書少淨係知飲管"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:32:50.000Z","msg":"我喺香港兩個都有聽開<br />\n唔知吸管係咪蝗語<br />\n如果係嘅唔好意思 我錯"},{"pid":"816f003aafd07a28abf162f11bbce8882a3950aa","tid":795271,"uid":98477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:38:32.000Z","msg":"真環保撚係非不得已唔會用膠類產品，我身邊有唔少呢類人。佢地生活係好唔方便，但係佢地又生活到。<br />\n<br />\n至於商家話要環保，所以唔提供某啲物品，好多時係要控制成本同做好品牌形象。"},{"pid":"6540009bce5e898bd4b48eda55cd76c9c1d285de","tid":795271,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:47:23.000Z","msg":"唔撚食佢最環保，又唔撚係有益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45aa4f781fe0ded6153e8750ee53a3649b3b0766","tid":795271,"uid":80413,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:53:02.000Z","msg":"飲管似係咁多樣入面無咁必要既餐具<br />\n同埋刀叉個啲無得唔派，除非商家肯轉用非即棄"},{"pid":"5bc1aa829e208c71127ee975c377a793cae1cde9","tid":795271,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:54:41.000Z","msg":"為地球應結紮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abfa07f5c6622db0e3f2d5ca5823a58a8b524333","tid":795271,"uid":53498,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"93adac38e82c590efc245f56ed22c8fd0499db51","tid":795271,"uid":10998,"like":20,"dislike":3,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:25:17.000Z","msg":"咩叫吸管？<br />\n<br />\n讀得書少淨係知飲管"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T02:01:43.000Z","msg":"叫開飲筒"},{"pid":"2a1bd65b5a527ee9a784835954d233ae107a2d71","tid":795271,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af675bba6f04fe9ac879920edc14ce7dd2833a6a","tid":795271,"uid":180156,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:21:15.000Z","msg":"其實商家點解要理會環保撚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T03:27:27.000Z","msg":"慳錢兼拎光環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19059e35592ac79d627040ad5bd0959d01e8d375","tid":795271,"uid":33868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T03:28:23.000Z","msg":"我都想問點解唔比飲管<br />\n但繼續用膠碗、膠叉、膠刀"},{"pid":"b139f82213bd4978c262161a31c2176ba80e8c80","tid":795271,"uid":11260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T03:36:37.000Z","msg":"膠對海洋破壞最大，分解時間都較長。<br />\n<br />\n至於點解只係唔派膠飲管，可能並非必要食用工具，同埋唔能夠一刀切一次過全部唔派。但小弟支持大方向係慢慢減少膠廢物。"},{"pid":"a747e151cad3a715f3184f886bdb66b0464cf17e","tid":795271,"uid":130568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b139f82213bd4978